For Christmas I suggested that family buy a toy for my dog instead of getting me anything this year.
I ended up with a three month BarkBox subscription!
It was an unexpected and unique gift.
I didn’t know that you could buy a subscription as a gift until I received it.

I decided to show what I received each month for fun.
I’ll update this post as I receive more boxes.
I picked the large dog option since my dog is 80+ pounds.
Each box has a given theme.

