This box contained two toys: a stuffed party hat with a squeaker inside and a rope with two stuffed mittens that also contained squeakers.
There were 3 food items: a pork chew, mac and cheese favored treats, and prime rib flavored treats.
Yum!
The party hat toy was made of especially durable fabric.
The mittens less so, but it’d expect them to last for my dog.
Viira likes to rip stuffing out gradually over time, but I could see this toy being destroyed quickly by some other dogs.
The food all seemed to be decent quality as well.
No complaints from myself or Viira!

